508.title: Barrack Banner.sea
508.author: Anonymous
508.description: This is a ResEdit file that contains a new score display for Barrack. The creator took the liberty of rearranging the display in a way he felt was more logical. ResEdit is required.

509.title: Barrack Discretion.sea
509.author: Anonymous
509.description: Barrack Discretion allows you permanently change two sounds in Barrack that some may find objectionable or not suitable for children. The two sounds are: "Oh My God" and "Shiiiiii".
